Name: Major League Baseball 2K9
Overview: Play ball!  Active roster updates guarantee your game is current.  2K Sports adds to its impressive library of player-specific animations with more than 300 new signature animations.  Right stick pitching, batting and responsive fielding brings your virtual baseball experience into the next generation.  Take charge of your franchise and enjoy the all-new MLB.com presentation style, a new level of CPU customization, multi-player functionality, and real player ambitions.  Inside Edge produces remarkably accurate player tendencies.  All-new Virtual Directory and commentary team brings in-game broadcasts to life in real-time like never before.  Featuring Judas Priest, Cheap Trick, Coheed & Cambria, SR-71, The Romantics, Boys Like Girls, and Europe.
